{"tid":1673671,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過或識人試過夢遊？","createTime":"2019-10-24T19:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T16:51:29.000Z","uid":283071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88d13bce6429d81d3362848d7253bac8163c6551","tid":1673671,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:05:25.000Z","msg":"細個識過一個朋友 係夢遊而跌落街死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞應該仲搵到 講真同佢唔熟好熟<br />\n但從此 夢遊呢個病 係我心目中變得好恐怖<br />\n好怕自己有一日夢遊左都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人試過夢遊或見過人夢遊?<br />\n夢遊既人會做d咩行為?<br />\n如果我叫醒夢遊既人  佢地會唔會聽到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b05895c5105ce7f0c84c5b37f65b38d66e0ffed","tid":1673671,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbYpESe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbYpESe.jpg&h=6c0e53db&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6aa8d67f1111be428a5983f5ec5d4796b5d1ad98","tid":1673671,"uid":251336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"一直都有夢遊症 <br />\n夜晚瞓覺會自己起身切生果食<br />\n食完仲要洗埋 啲碗碗碟碟<br />\n睇返屋企Cctv 先知"},{"pid":"4515804c3232c0d01a24a41c4a1a09668e48471b","tid":1673671,"uid":227719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T19:39:47.000Z","msg":"我自己有<br />\n都係屋企人同我講先知<br />\n<br />\n細個果時訓訓下教 落咗床 行咗出屋企門口<br />\n好彩我腳步聲夠大 嘈醒咗屋企人<br />\n先至捉返我入屋企<br />\n<br />\n直到第二朝訓醒 佢地同番我講先知<br />\n<br />\n之後又試過夜媽媽 係廳嗰度不停兜圈行<br />\n<br />\n諗返都覺得幾恐怖"},{"pid":"aeff27d014087eab1055d6d99193ccec971a22d1","tid":1673671,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T21:01:20.000Z","msg":"人生試過惟一一次<br />\n起身坐左係沙發到 坐到屋企人痾夜尿叫我先有番意識<br />\n<br />\n你當好似飲酒斷片咁"},{"pid":"9ad63c280f03508c17951a5432176efd0ab09696","tid":1673671,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco